\par }{\b\f0\insrsid866943 In the early stages was there a feeling that actually this could become a problem?
\par 
\par }{\f0\insrsid866943 Not initially.  We just kept fingers crossed and hoped that it wouldn\rquote t.  We weren\rquote 
