\par 
\par The day that they said they were going to do the cull, that was just an absolute nightmare [EMPHASIS], and
 in fact, me and my colleagues, we just broke into tears, we just said that means our village is going to be wiped out if this is going to happen; because when we [EMPHASIS]  heard it was going to be everything [EMPHASIS], but on the way home in the car w
